data.description: Welcome to 20 Mallard Trail! Situated in the pristine setting of Carolina Lakes gated community! This home boasts two stories with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The formal dining and living rooms have beautiful hardwood floors, and plenty of space for hosting. The kitchen offers wood cabinets, granite counter tops and an island that makes for a welcoming entertaining area. French doors  lead you into the enclosed carolina room. Upstairs you will find four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master has tray ceilings, a private bathroom with duel vanities, a jacuzzi tub and large walk in closet.  Outside you will love the large deck and fully fenced in yard, along with an additional fenced in dog run! Oversized garage and additional cement with extra parking for a boat! Home backs to a wooded area for more privacy. 1.5 mile nature trail borders the backyard.  Enjoy 24 hour guarded entrance, community pool, 7 lakes, beach, marina & golf course!  Play grounds, Tennis Courts, Basketball Courts, Softball Field.  SELLER HAS A 3.75% RATE FOR A POSSIBLE ASSUMPTION WITH ANOTHER VETERAN!Over $20,000 in upgrades including the roof and the AC unit! Schedule your showings today!
